{/* Desktop */}

Conclusion and Next Steps

The redesigned personal account dashboard improved user experience and business results by simplifying navigation, adding payment management, and showcasing exclusive offers. This reduced support inquiries, boosted user engagement, and increased upsell and partner deal conversions, driving revenue growth.

Next Steps:

  • Mobile Optimization: Enhance the mobile experience for users primarily on mobile devices.
  • User Feedback Loops: Implement in-app surveys for ongoing insights and continuous dashboard improvement.
  • Referral System: Launch a referral program to reward users for bringing in new customers, boosting acquisition and loyalty.
